eg;V</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#e9f6ff\" style=\"padding-right: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.25pt; font-size: 12px; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; line-height: 150%; padding-top: 2.25pt; font-family: verdana\">亮度(典型值)</td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#e9f6ff\" style=\"padding-right: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.25pt; font-size: 12px; border-left-color: #3b87ce; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; line-height: 150%; padding-top: 2.25pt; font-family: verdana; border-left-style: solid; word-wrap: break-word\">250cd/m2</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" width=\"33%\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"padding-right: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.25pt; font-size: 12px; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; line-height: 150%; padding-top: 2.25pt; font-family: verdana\">对比度(典型值)</td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-right: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.25pt; font-size: 12px; border-left-color: #3b87ce; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; line-height: 150%; padding-top: 2.25pt; font-family: verdana; border-left-style: solid; background-color: white; word-wrap: break-word\">5000:1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#e9f6ff\" style=\"padding-right: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.25pt; font-size: 12px; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; line-height: 150%; padding-top: 2.25pt; font-family: verdana\">动态对比度</td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#e9f6ff\" style=\"padding-right: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.25pt; font-size: 12px; border-left-color: #3b87ce; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; line-height: 150%; padding-top: 2.25pt; font-family: verdana; border-left-style: solid; word-wrap: break-word\">2000W:1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" width=\"33%\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"padding-right: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.25pt; font-size: 12px; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; line-height: 150%; padding-top: 2.25pt; font-family: verdana\">响应时间</td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-right: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.25pt; font-size: 12px; border-left-color: #3b87ce; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; line-height: 150%; padding-top: 2.25pt; font-family: verdana; border-left-style: solid; background-color: white; word-wrap: break-word\">4ms（GTG）</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#e9f6ff\" style=\"padding-right: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.25pt; font-size: 12px; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; line-height: 150%; padding-top: 2.25pt; font-family: verdana\">点距</td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#e9f6ff\" style=\"padding-right: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.25pt; font-size: 12px; border-left-color: #3b87ce; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; line-height: 150%; padding-top: 2.25pt; font-family: verdana; border-left-style: solid; word-wrap: break-word\">0.248mm</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"padding-right: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.25pt; font-size: 12px; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; line-height: 150%; padding-top: 2.25pt; font-family: verdana\">面板类型</td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-right: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.25pt; font-size: 12px; border-left-color: #3b87ce; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; line-height: 150%; padding-top: 2.25pt; font-family: verdana; border-left-style: solid; background-color: white; word-wrap: break-word\">MVA</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#e9f6ff\" style=\"padding-right: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.25pt; font-size: 12px; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; line-height: 150%; padding-top: 2.25pt; font-family: verdana\">接口</td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#e9f6ff\" style=\"padding-right: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.25pt; font-size: 12px; border-left-color: #3b87ce; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; line-height: 150%; padding-top: 2.25pt; font-family: verdana; border-left-style: solid; word-wrap: break-word\">D-sub / DVI-D</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>明基GW2250显示器作为GW2240M升级版本，沿用了其成熟外观工艺，超窄圆弧边框结合黑亮钢琴烤漆使其典雅稳健气质彰显无遗。显示器左下角印制明基独有的senseye3色彩技术及<a target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#666666\">LED</font></a>背光源标志，突出其卓越的色彩能力和环保节能的使用体验。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center\"><a target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/172/BE1IZEZ2QZAH_B0KEN5FI35T4_IMG_2416_500_500.jpg\" /></a><a target=\"_blank\"><br />\r\n<img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/3WZS8Y855WE8_IMG_2429_250.JPG\" /></a><a target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/N24ZMD50DJTX_IMG_2428_250.JPG\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left\">显示器背面为经典G系列背板设计，大面积散热孔紧密贴合在机身上方高效散出机身热量。背板中保留了四个挂壁孔位，方便安装在支架中将显示器竖立使用。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/9X29Q185J14L_IMG_2419_500.JPG\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left\">由于采用LED背光源，GW2250侧面轻盈纤薄，能够支持大约25&deg;左右的角度变换，适合不同坐高用户使用。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/93Q22E870CF6_IMG_2421_250.JPG\" /></a><a target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/C476GS11TN56_IMG_2420_250.JPG\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>由经典背部模具打造，散热孔上方仍印制着明基LOGO。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/V0V8LMZK66VQ_IMG_2422_500.JPG\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left\">显示器OSD控件处于边框右下角，采用六键控制，适合右手用户使用，在<a target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#666666\">电源</font></a>按键处特别安装了<a target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#666666\">LED</font></a>灯，以便用户在黑暗环境中判断显示器的工作状态和按键方位。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/KXJ343R4K8R0_IMG_2427_500.JPG\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left\">显示器包含两大主流接口，SUB-D和DVI-D，能够轻松应付日常娱乐和工作。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/4M8BTA910LO9_IMG_2423_500.JPG\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>亮度、色度测试</strong></p>\r\n<p>首先使用比较知名的ColorFacts显示专业软件配合显示器菜单的RGB调色菜单对其进行调色处理，使其RGB三原色达到尽可能的平衡。以便使显示器达到最佳工作状态。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/01A4J2V7W29M_1_500.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left\">调整完毕后，我们预热半个小时后进行了色温，亮度等测试。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 对于ANSI对比度，我们采用16点黑白相间色块，8个白色区域亮度平均值和8个黑色区域亮度平均值之间比值，通过测量局部峰值亮度和底值亮度，能有效的避免伪动态背光技术可能带来的干扰。计算黑白数值均值即可得出实际对比度。我们测试到的ANSI对比度达到了1007：1。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/FG81N870585Z_500.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在色域测试方面，测试软件通过显示RGB三原色，然后详细记<a target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#666666\">录屏</font></a>幕中间点的色度值。在色度空间上R、G、B三点围成的三角形区域就是显示器可以显示的全部颜色区域，这一区域的面积与NTSC 1953定义的RGB色彩范围的面积之比就是色彩饱和度得分。测到的数据色彩范围大约为75.9%NTSC，由于设备存在误差，测试结果可能有一些浮动。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/U12DF2E8B405_5_500.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 关于白色不均匀性，这款产品的均匀度达到了84%，是一款色彩均匀性不错的产品。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left\"><strong>灰度色阶测试</strong></p>\r\n<p>灰度、色阶方面的测试一直是<a target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#666666\">液晶显示器</font></a>的重要考量参考，用来评价液晶显示器的灰阶过度能力，以及黑白转换能力等。越是明显的反差表示液晶显示器处理色彩画面的能力越强。以下屏摄结果仅供参考。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/D6G0724I86AN_IMG_1017_500.JPG\" /><br />\r\n32位黑白色阶测试</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/Q5Q7C3235F0A_IMG_1020_500.JPG\" /><br />\r\n256位黑白色阶测试</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left\"><strong>&nbsp; 色彩过渡测试</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;色彩过渡方面，我们对显示器的色彩横向和竖向过度进行了测试，以下屏摄结果仅供参考。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/YM653THA2HH3_1IMG_4500_500.jpg\" /><br />\r\n纯色色阶横行过度测试</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/QT5K99594T9N_1IMG_4504_500.jpg\" /><br />\r\n纯色色阶竖行过度测试</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/Z0G822315Y76_1IMG_4506_500.jpg\" /><br />\r\n多色块过渡测试</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left\">高清屏摄一</p>\r\n<p>第一部屏摄影片采用火热悬疑动作片《命运规划局》。此片为快节奏1080p高清分辨率影片，片中掺杂丰富明暗快速切换，对显示器的屏幕响应速度和动态对比度都是很好的考验。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/172/5K4CPIJIX042_DSC_0981_500.JPG\" /><br />\r\n屏摄画面一</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/172/2Z3M32D3663N_DSC_0982_500.JPG\" /><br />\r\n屏摄画面二</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/172/HX4F91V4YA74_DSC_0983_500.JPG\" /><br />\r\n屏摄画面三</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/172/YRF13Y0H6047_DSC_0979_500.JPG\" /><br />\r\n屏摄画面四</p>\r\n<p>明暗对比的快速场景处理是明基黑锐丽屏一贯优势，高速相应速度配合广视角MVA屏应对此片可说是游刃有余。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left\">高清屏摄二：</p>\r\n<p>另一部高清片源我们选择了1080p的《坏中尉》，此片为深色调动作片，片中包含大量明暗现场的对比，及浅色场景切换，能够比较直观的观测显示器在对比度和色彩方面的表现能力。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/172/SV2LD2154836_DSC_0984_500.JPG\" /><br />\r\n屏摄画面一</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/172/7RD082VZ8U88_DSC_0985_500.JPG\" /><br />\r\n屏摄画面二</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/172/37JD0686JUA5_DSC_0986_500.JPG\" /><br />\r\n屏摄画面三</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/172/DIW9PYR3EJ6F_DSC_0987_500.JPG\" /><br />\r\n屏摄画面四</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left\">在此片中，明基黑锐丽显示器表现优异，既能很好诠释片中深色调宏大场景，有着重突出了浅色场景中丰富的色彩对比，相比同价位产品有明显优势。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left\">众所周知，<a target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#666666\">LED</font></a>背光源的优势之一既是其极低的工作能耗，相比同类CCFL显示器产品，LED背光源显示器能够节省10%-30%的工作能耗。在常用亮度工作情况下，我们测量了使用LED背光源的明基GW2250，其耗电仅为24.94w，是一款出色的节能产品。此款产品也获得了ecoFACTS、能源之星等多项认证。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/171/3PQ06MP4487L_IMG_2471_500.JPG\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><a target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"黑锐丽屏强势再袭 明基GW2250显示器评测\" _ks_lazy_height=\"92\" _ks_lazy_width=\"92\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom: 1px solid\" src=\"http://image.tianjimedia.com/uploadImages/2012/172/3X7G22M5YLT2_92234AR0E7SU_IMG_2417_500_500.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>编辑点评：明基GW2250是一款适合家庭或商务入门用户使用的广视角显示器产品，采用专业级广视角&ldquo;黑锐丽屏&rdquo;，在色彩、色域、对比度上完全可媲美E-IPS显示面板，而价格却更平易近人。在屏幕漏光控制、响应速度及高动态对比度上，黑锐丽屏更是有传统IPS无法抗衡的优势性能，从而打造出栩栩如生的细腻动态画面。</p>','images/201306/thumb_img/2533_thumb_G_1370239019219.jpg','images/201306/goods_img/2533_G_1370239019027.jpg','images/201306/source_img/2533_G_1370239019014.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1370239019','100','0','1','0','1','0','0','1373801293','6','','0','0','0','0');
