ottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-style: normal; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 272.25pt; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; height: 14.25pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: middle; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; font-weight: 400; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0px\">最大VGA分辨率：2048x1536</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/1030494238/T26Q9uXn0bXXXXXXXX_!!1030494238.png\" /></p>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" src=\"http://china.zotac.com/media/product/508f9aaca3373.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n<h4 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.33em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">支持Microsoft&reg; DirectX&reg; 11</h4>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">这款DirectX 11 GPU支持Shader Model 3.1，专为提供超高性能而设计，可满足曲面细分（Tessellation）GPU加速功能的需要，曲面细分是DirectX 11这一全新API中的关键图形特性。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" src=\"http://china.zotac.com/media/product/508e282ba4c03.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.33em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">英伟达自适应垂直同步</h4>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">没有什么事情能够比帧速率迟滞和屏幕撕裂效果更令玩家分心。 前者出现在帧速率较低的时候，而当帧速率过高时又会出现后者的情形。 自适应垂直同步在帧渲染方面是一种更加智能的方法。 在高帧速率时，启用垂直同步以消除撕裂效果；而在低帧速率时，则禁用垂直同步以最大限度减少迟滞。 它可以摆脱令人分心的情形，让用户能够专心享受游戏体验。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" src=\"http://china.zotac.com/media/product/508f9a7ca792b.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.33em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">英伟达 CUDA 技术</h4>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">英伟达 CUDA 技术可释放 GPU 中众多处理核心的强大能力来加速照片编辑等最棘手的系统任务，与传统 CPU 相比，能够实现惊人的性能提升。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" src=\"http://china.zotac.com/media/product/508f9afb3ea80.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.33em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">英伟达PhysX技术</h4>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">这款英伟达精视（GeForce）GPU完全支持英伟达PhysX技术，在游戏中可实现物理效果互动的全新境界，从而能够带来更加生动逼真的体验。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" src=\"http://china.zotac.com/media/product/508f9abec43a2.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.33em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">HDMI</h4>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">支持HDMI，其中包括 GPU 加速的蓝光 3D 支持、x.v.色彩、HDMI 深色以及 7.1 数字环绕声。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" src=\"http://china.zotac.com/media/product/508f9acf44392.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.33em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">支持PCI Express 2.0</h4>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">本产品专为全新PCI Express 2.0总线架构设计，可为最需带宽支持的游戏与3D应用程序提供最快的数据传输速度，同时兼容现有PCI Express主板，保持了向后的兼容性，提供了最广泛的支持。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-