1028659449.jpg\" /></a></span></div>\r\n            <div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n            <div>\r\n            <table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"750\" align=\"center\" style=\"border-bottom-color: black; text-align: left; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; border-spacing: 0px; display: table; border-collapse: separate; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black\">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td width=\"442\" style=\"border-bottom-color: black; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0)\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">一、使用USB2.0线接产品使用方法：</span></strong></span></div>\r\n                        <div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0)\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">1.硬盘</strong></span></span></div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0)\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 将移动硬盘或光驱接入产品的相应接口。</span></span></div>\r\n                        <div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0)\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">2.电源</span></strong></span></div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0)\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 该产品附带DC电源，将电源DC头接入产品的电源接口，另一端接电源插座，</span></span></div>\r\n                        <div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0)\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">3.线</span></strong></span></div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0)\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 将USB2.0线的迷你5Pin端口接入产品的USB端口，另一端USB公头良好接入主机主板的USB母头（如果是PC机，建议接入主板的USB端口）</span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td height=\"210\" width=\"360\" style=\"border-bottom-color: black; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0)\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/1028659449/T26OV8XbXcXXXXXXXX_!!1028659449.jpg\" /></span></span></td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            <table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"750\" align=\"center\" style=\"border-bottom-color: black; text-align: left; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; border-spacing: 0px; display: table; border-collapse: separate; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black\">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td style=\"border-bottom-color: black; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n                        <div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0)\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0)\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">4.打开排插开关</span></strong></span></span></div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0)\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 此时产品电源指示灯呈红色常亮状态。IDE和SATA接口的LED指示灯呈蓝色常亮